at the bottom of Tokyo Bay.

236
00:19:01,871 --> 00:19:05,140
Huh?

237
00:19:05,141 --> 00:19:07,243
(shouts)

238
00:19:13,616 --> 00:19:16,386
(high-pitch hum)

239
00:19:18,221 --> 00:19:20,156
- That kid's a monster!

240
00:19:21,825 --> 00:19:22,825
- [Bunshichi] Shin.

241
00:19:28,064 --> 00:19:29,064
- Hey, Shin.

242
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:36,839
- Mitsuomi, sorry about that.

243
00:19:38,174 --> 00:19:41,210
I was lookin over my shoulder
out of my patched eye.

244
00:19:41,211 --> 00:19:43,212
You caught me in my blind spot

245
00:19:43,213 --> 00:19:45,414
and when I finally
recognized who you were

246
00:19:45,415 --> 00:19:46,616
it was too late.

247
00:19:49,352 --> 00:19:50,652
- Big brother!

248
00:19:50,653 --> 00:19:52,354
- I figured that.

249
00:19:52,355 --> 00:19:55,091
I realize that it was
all just an accident.

250
00:20:00,930 --> 00:20:02,065
What else could it be?

251
00:20:06,536 --> 00:20:08,036
- [Maya] At that moment

252
00:20:08,037 --> 00:20:11,940
the only thing I was concerned
with was Mitsuomi's health.

253
00:20:11,941 --> 00:20:15,043
The fact that my brother
was crumbling before my eyes

254
00:20:15,044 --> 00:20:17,212
was lost on me.

255
00:20:17,213 --> 00:20:19,815
Mitsuomi was all
that I worried about.

256
00:20:19,816 --> 00:20:21,116
- [Shin] How about you, Maya?

257
00:20:21,117 --> 00:20:22,085
You all right?

258
00:20:22,086 --> 00:20:23,518
(smacks)

259
00:20:23,519 --> 00:20:25,021
- [Maya] Mitsuomi!

260
00:20:27,323 --> 00:20:28,323
- Hm?

261
00:20:29,525 --> 00:20:32,127
- [Maya] If only I didn't
scream when Mitsuomi

262
00:20:32,128 --> 00:20:34,029
entered the classroom.

263
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:36,531
Maybe his fate would've
been different.

264
00:20:36,532 --> 00:20:37,966
The Dragon's Eye.

265
00:20:37,967 --> 00:20:38,967
The Reiki.

266
00:20:38,968 --> 00:20:40,202
Destiny.

267
00:20:40,203 --> 00:20:42,237
None of these things
are the problem.

268
00:20:42,238 --> 00:20:44,540
- [Mitsuomi] What's up,
is something wrong, Maya?

269
00:20:46,109 --> 00:20:49,177
- [Maya] I'm the fire that's
devouring my big brother.

270
00:20:49,178 --> 00:20:50,946
You should go away!

271
00:20:50,947 --> 00:20:53,715
You shouldn't have
anything to do with me!

272
00:20:53,716 --> 00:20:55,817
I tried to tell him that.

273
00:20:55,818 --> 00:20:58,520
I tried to get those
words out of my mouth.

274
00:20:58,521 --> 00:21:00,122
But they wouldn't come.

275
00:21:00,123 --> 00:21:02,023
No matter how hard I tried.

276
00:21:02,024 --> 00:21:04,026
They just stayed
caught in my throat.

277
00:21:09,065 --> 00:21:14,070
(somber music)

278
00:21:36,792 --> 00:21:38,861
(groans)

279
00:21:51,641 --> 00:21:55,444
("Aishiene Motto")

280
00:23:22,498 --> 00:23:24,098
- [Voiceover] What
one hears is destiny

281
00:23:24,099 --> 00:23:26,000
showering down like rain.

282
00:23:26,001 --> 00:23:29,103
What one sees is the
deep river of shadows.

283
00:23:29,104 --> 00:23:31,139
Next episode of "Tenjou Tenge"

284
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:32,607
"Determination".

285
00:23:32,608 --> 00:23:35,444
You've got to do it, you've
got to stop these tears!

